Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世之初 冥冥之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning, there was darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着一声爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上 液体就在我们周围\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On Earth, liquids are all around us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至在我们体内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even inside of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我们的世界却与众不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But our world is not like others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们举目浩瀚宇宙间的恒星及行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we look at the stars and planets of our vast cosmos,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,液体其实是相当罕见的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}liquids are actually very rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们发现有液体时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when we do find liquids,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其怪模怪样地流动在怪异的世界里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they flow in strange ways, on bizarre worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种环境是我们在地球上无法创造的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's an environment where nothing that we can build here on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是片刻都无法承受的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could withstand that for more than a fraction of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新发现将永远改变我们对我们液体宇宙的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}New discoveries are forever changing what we know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻腾 沸腾问题的认识\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about the churning, bubbling matter of our liquid universe.
